rComments: This prof is very intelligent. However, his lectures are painful. Unless you read the book you will not understand them if you do not have prior knowledge of the subject matter. He will go on and on without having a clear guideline throughout the lecture. Also his train of thought is incomprehensible. If you read the book though you might enjoy it.
